    <section id="id3698162">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id3637853"><emphasis effect="bold">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis> The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent patterns and relationships, as well as to solve problems using algebraic language and skills.</para>
      <para id="id3707976"><emphasis effect="bold">Assessment Standard 1.10:</emphasis> We know this when the learner uses a range of techniques to perform written and mental calculations with whole numbers including:</para>
      <para id="id3495296"><emphasis effect="bold">1.10.3:</emphasis> building up and breaking down numbers</para>
